Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.25,0:01:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可思议世界之谜逐渐被解开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.82,0:01:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一而再，再而三地掌控\N『奇妙有趣的世界』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.13,0:01:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是由萨希脑中所涌现出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.20,0:01:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换言之，不管小步多么希望\N回到原来的阿倍野桥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.00,0:01:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但因萨希的缘故而老是回不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.01,0:01:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而这就是无法由\N“奇妙有趣的世界中”摆脱的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.88,0:02:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是因为知道原因了\N所以这次没问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.62,0:02:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二人的心意合而为一\N这次一定能成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.95,0:02:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但事实又如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.23,0:02:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希若永远处于这样的世界中\N那又会如何呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.70,0:02:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种搞不清楚明天的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.54,0:02:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想回到平常大家居住的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.74,0:02:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且也希望能考虑到家人朋友\N还有萨希的事情…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.65,0:02:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.21,0:02:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是一回到原来的阿倍野桥的话\N小步就要搬走了，搬到北海道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.07,0:02:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.07,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.03,0:02:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.91,0:03:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的，不管怎么看\N都是极现实的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.78,0:03:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有机器人、没有恐龙…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.52,0:03:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不用看小步爸爸和秋姐的表情\N不用上学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.99,0:03:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.96,0:03:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了\N回到原来的阿倍野桥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.16,0:03:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈！小步，你看你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小步？小步…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小步她消失到哪里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管如此，这里是高中校园吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.51,0:03:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底在搞什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.09,0:03:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…要迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.86,0:03:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.03,0:03:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等！搞什么嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但能与这么可爱的女生牵手\N是何等幸福啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.77,0:04:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔…这种触感是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一大早在吵什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.57,0:04:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是木奈木奈！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.51,0:04:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿那种服装上学\N生活指导老师会生气哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.31,0:04:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到保健室来一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.38,0:04:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木奈木奈出现的话…\N那这里并非原来的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过仅管如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.69,0:04:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里全是些超可爱的女生\N在大阪绝对想像不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真伤脑筋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.40,0:04:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈！真是超幸运！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.31,0:04:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第8话 心跳！\N阿倍野桥☆学园商店街
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.28,0:04:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了…这样就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.45,0:04:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么脸红呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.89,0:04:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为…因为…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.62,0:04:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希的心意很令人高兴\N但老师已经心有所属了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.33,0:05:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呜…他现在在何方呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人在意那种事情的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.10,0:05:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以萨希只好请你忍耐点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.50,0:05:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点都没在听人家讲的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.91,0:05:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…梦想的世界\N能置身此地真好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.94,0:05:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…痛…啊！萨希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小步？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.52,0:05:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.19,0:05:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.63,0:05:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.86,0:05:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你会变成这副Q版模样\N这是你的嗜好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.97,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会是嗜好\N为什么我会变成这副模样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.87,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么回不到原来的世界？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.14,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为什么呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.14,0:05:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这完全与我无关
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然有关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之所以会来到这种世界\N除了你的缘故以外还有谁…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.15,0:05:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可爱…跑哪去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.78,0:05:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草字头加上“明”是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萌（萌芽）…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你头壳没坏掉吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.92,0:06:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小可爱、小可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.63,0:06:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的初恋\N真希望自己就是她所疼爱的宠物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.83,0:06:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！小可爱、小可爱！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.67,0:06:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.25,0:06:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,墨镜的鸡嘴、鸡冠真是无与伦比\N（胡言乱语中）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么，小步也来啦\N太好了，太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.42,0:06:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎还能心平气和地上课呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.22,0:06:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不设法快点离开这样的世界\N还在做什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.19,0:06:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再等一等，才刚到而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.49,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留在此地一定会有好处的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.30,0:06:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你一脸白痴相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.90,0:06:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定是想认识\N刚刚那个可爱女孩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.37,0:06:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那种下流想法\N我一看就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何你会知道呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.44,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎会不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.74,0:06:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.68,0:07:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从之前的模式来看就知道\N绝对不会让我们这么悠闲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.92,0:07:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正我爸爸与雅萨爷爷必定会\N穿着水手服绑着辫子追来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.43,0:07:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是想就令人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.83,0:07:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.86,0:07:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.20,0:07:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.90,0:07:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.97,0:07:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛叫的那么亲蜜…\N她是傻瓜吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.14,0:07:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才刚转学进来\N还没有教科书吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.87,0:07:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起看吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了，请看！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萌芽、萌芽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.85,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样看着人家，真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.78,0:07:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.72,0:07:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.82,0:07:39.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请翻开到第74页
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.29,0:07:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希你翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…亚美你翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.69,0:07:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.69,0:07:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚美啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.73,0:07:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚美啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.70,0:07:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚美啦…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来翻啦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.00,0:07:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！大家请注意\N这烤面包为何会那么好吃呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！萨希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.91,0:08:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.08,0:08:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这小鬼说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.88,0:08:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这烤面包为何会好吃呢？\N那是因为…大家听好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.58,0:08:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是大家爱面包的缘故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.99,0:08:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.52,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.86,0:08:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起去中庭吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.46,0:08:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.03,0:08:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？卖完了啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.66,0:08:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子，大家都是好孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.57,0:08:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.14,0:08:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个，给你吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.31,0:08:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本想与你一起吃的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.82,0:08:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚美和阿熏相较下\N萨希比较喜欢谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.99,0:08:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个三心二意的笨蛋要被甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，我没那个意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，绝对不原谅你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…怎会！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了，死心吧死心吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚美对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了，已经结束了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了，我不在乎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使萨希喜欢上别的女生\N亚美对你的心意还是不会变的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.94,0:09:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么一开始就别哭嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.78,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真令人感动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.91,0:09:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你感动个什么颈…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.88,0:09:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唯独有件事要遵守约定…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.15,0:09:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使转学到全国任何一地\N最后结局就算死掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.99,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也不能忘记我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.09,0:09:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.16,0:09:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么情形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.49,0:09:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂，萨希！\N别太过份，别太过份哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.36,0:09:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有没听到我说的话！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.33,0:09:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.03,0:09:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.90,0:09:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真过份…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.40,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.07,0:09:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那么，我还有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.75,0:09:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希，明天见！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，明天见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.15,0:09:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.68,0:09:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.15,0:09:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.22,0:09:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！出现了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.29,0:09:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,救…救命啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.46,0:09:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等，是我是我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.02,0:09:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛，原来是小步啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.69,0:10:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然你以为是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腐烂的木乃伊或鬼怪什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.33,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想知道是腐烂的木乃伊\N鬼怪比较可怕还是我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.30,0:10:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.27,0:10:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道怕了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.44,0:10:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而你真的没事吗？\N怎么看都像是快死了一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.74,0:10:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于人而言健康最重要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.51,0:10:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错…别抢我的台词！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快想办法回到原来世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但又还没找到小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.58,0:10:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就快点找出来呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我长角了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.72,0:10:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么『是啊』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.92,0:10:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何不早点告诉我\N笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.33,0:10:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.69,0:10:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样太勉强了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.53,0:10:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不试看看怎会知道呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.16,0:10:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.80,0:10:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托能让我们回到原来世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.64,0:10:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我知道了…事实上\N真的需要一些供品才行的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.78,0:10:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我已经很放下身段地做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.52,0:10:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么这次一定要想着\N回到原来世界才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.35,0:10:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.09,0:11:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么要走了喔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇！不知怎么搞的居然生效了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.90,0:11:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.77,0:11:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,存在这世上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.64,0:11:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有天尊神明与地尊神明啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.37,0:11:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,急急如律令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.02,0:11:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了！回到原来世界了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.86,0:11:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想有另一个小鬼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.20,0:11:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.70,0:11:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要迟到了要迟到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.73,0:11:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，哥哥\N不快一点的话就要迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？你不是萨希的姐姐吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.91,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！附带一提…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在Config画面的称呼方法\N请从哥哥、大哥、兄、内兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.28,0:11:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家兄、兄长、大哥哥、干哥\N老兄、哥、小哥、老哥、阿哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.95,0:12:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等13个种类中\N选择你所喜欢并记录下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.92,0:12:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么啊…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！要迟到了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.56,0:12:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又不等我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.89,0:12:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希，早安！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.43,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼，这样的世界太乱了\N等着瞧，萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.88,0:12:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧地叫你出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.81,0:12:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾经帮我找寻我的小可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.92,0:12:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在福利社前\N还对你那么冷淡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.22,0:12:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，没关系没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.22,0:12:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，你没错\N我突然叫住你也有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.16,0:12:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我想与你约会\N改变你的印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.50,0:12:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很为难吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.90,0:12:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎会为难！要去哪？要去哪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.84,0:12:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.84,0:12:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天忘了戴隐形眼镜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼…眼镜小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.14,0:13:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萌芽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戴眼镜时这样最轻松了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更强烈的触觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激烈萌芽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.09,0:13:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.00,0:13:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕的话就抓住我的手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.27,0:13:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（恶魔召唤全集，使用说明书）\N五分钟学会，附泡汤须知事典
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.90,0:13:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蚯蚓、青蛙对不起了\N公车、电车全都停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.51,0:13:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月亮也被云遮住\N关紧遮雨篷、小孩全都睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.38,0:13:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒来吧！魔物们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.88,0:13:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,【法】早安，主人有何吩咐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀…来了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.82,0:13:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.52,0:13:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了！你们二人！\N去把萨希给我抓来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.43,0:13:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.83,0:13:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别…别过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腰…我的腰…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.64,0:14:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的，那两个老傢伙搞什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真吵呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛，原来还有啊！\N别吓我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.15,0:14:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，尽情地修理他们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.29,0:14:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.76,0:14:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（三分钟让你轻松成为军事专家）\N特别附录泡茶须知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此原来如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.48,0:14:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次一定要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受死吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.99,0:15:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现最早出现的星星了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好坏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.83,0:15:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…发现第二个星星了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.10,0:15:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的，啊\N第3颗…4、5、6…！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.41,0:15:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10、11、12、13\N14、15、16…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，有种不好的预感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.31,0:15:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万点繁星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何会这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.32,0:15:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.62,0:15:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多星星哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希！你没事吧！\N萨希…萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.13,0:15:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你终于醒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.00,0:15:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木奈木奈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.34,0:15:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她等好久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.70,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希，你没事了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.61,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你看见我出糗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.64,0:15:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，没那回事，没那回事！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.01,0:15:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希的勇气救了全世界…你看…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.45,0:16:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.69,0:16:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友都笑着对我说\N萨希好像超人一样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.30,0:16:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是朋友们都搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.90,0:16:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小熏…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.13,0:16:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你要多多自我保重\N因为萨希老是那样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的，我担心的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.04,0:16:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.08,0:16:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尸骨会好好放置在垃圾箱中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.68,0:16:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放在窗边的盆栽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.62,0:16:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！这样很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…放在窗边的桌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…放在窗边的黑板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.63,0:16:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把这种东西放在窗边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.60,0:16:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.54,0:16:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让萨希尝尝地狱的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.21,0:16:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.01,0:16:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.25,0:16:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小步？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.18,0:17:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.21,0:17:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎会好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.78,0:17:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样看起来像好吗\N你没看见我正倒大楣啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么不愉快之事吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.72,0:17:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这种愚蠢的世界中\N又怎会有快乐可言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到处全是些令人讨厌之事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.96,0:17:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌讨厌，真的很讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.23,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌这样的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小步…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.54,0:17:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.81,0:17:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.71,0:17:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上下课后\N小熏约我到告白之树下见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.21,0:17:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.88,0:17:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么解释呢…\N这才到另一个世界吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.79,0:17:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.85,0:17:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换言之，我认为在树下告白后\N就意味着游戏结束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.03,0:17:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既是如此的话\N真正的鬼便会出现才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.33,0:17:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.46,0:17:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听你这么一说似乎真有可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.73,0:17:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着我们拜托小鬼\N请他帮忙让我们回到原来世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要那么做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.94,0:18:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是当然的，我怎会留在\N让小步吃尽苦头的地方呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.38,0:18:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.58,0:18:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萨希？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.88,0:18:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.92,0:18:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若我下次再发生这种事的话…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.96,0:18:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.19,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一生一世都要待在这种地狱里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.13,0:18:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你很有心得…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他已经在那了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不过去吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.24,0:18:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.34,0:18:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起第一次与萨希相遇时\N也是撞了个正着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.48,0:18:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须得与萨希分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.85,0:18:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.62,0:18:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事实上我并不是个普通人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.36,0:18:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.46,0:18:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为时间已到，所以得返回天上\N谢谢你陪我那么久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.50,0:19:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃的鲷鱼烧很好吃…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.77,0:19:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提我真正的名字叫\NHMX12人型机器人，再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.11,0:19:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,角色全都混杂得乱七八糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃鲷鱼烧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.19,0:19:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藉由那样的事件\N能增加亚美的好感度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.06,0:19:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着或许会在我家守候\N然后因过于兴奋而过于激动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.99,0:19:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,产生触发事件，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.96,0:19:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了，太快了点吧！快回来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.63,0:19:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是该做这种事的时候吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.33,0:19:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小步，拜托你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.77,0:19:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不可以不要过关？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.41,0:19:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要让亚美和小熏变成如此？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.81,0:19:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，亚美也是个好女孩\N所以请再一次…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不敢奢求从头开始…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.68,0:19:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但至少能从稍早前\N希望能从重修旧好那时开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.25,0:19:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从鲷鱼烧的记录点开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.46,0:19:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我当成什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.09,0:20:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，萨希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.16,0:20:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.96,0:20:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你每天都尽幻想着傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.50,0:20:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们才会来到这莫名的世界\N真是智障
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.40,0:20:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了愿望只要一想到方法\N便打算不断重覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.88,0:20:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用手挖耳朵智商会降低的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.28,0:20:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何会变这样！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.99,0:20:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小步，小步，是我的错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回到原来的世界啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.23,0:20:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小步！我知道了，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.24,0:20:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦！萨希说的话完全没信用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.79,0:21:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跑掉了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.32,0:21:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太棒了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此世界经常出现呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.86,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,优达斯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.13,0:21:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这也需要拥有非凡的想像力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.50,0:21:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从刚被溢出的生命力中\N发现一股超现实的想像力…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真是不得了的小孩呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.04,0:21:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？觉得好像在被夸奖，我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.81,0:21:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而只有素质的话\N也不能怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.08,0:21:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何论理上的保证\N这是大亲教授论点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟在我身边多少还能做点科学…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.05,0:21:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科学？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.69,0:21:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也刚要回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.06,0:21:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜就住在我家吧\N我会告诉你科学性的思考吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.63,0:21:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是小步…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.20,0:21:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心，这也是缘份！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.71,0:22:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的缘份在科学体系中\N是最重要的元素…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.71,0:22:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一题会考吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.98,0:23:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小步巨大化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.82,0:23:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.18,0:23:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后小步去了哪里了呢？\N又发生什么事情了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.82,0:23:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，别问我啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.79,0:23:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但小步巨大化了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.59,0:23:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快做下回预告吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.03,0:23:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，对对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.86,0:23:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没上场的人向上场的人\N寻问接下来发生的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.90,0:23:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生什么事情呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.06,0:23:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.73,0:23:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.30,0:24:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但既是如此小步都已巨大化了\N为何现在还能与我再此闲谈呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.70,0:24:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别那么多理由了\N快做下回预告吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.17,0:24:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了\N接下来发生何事呢？
